library(tidyverse)  # v.1.3.0

## load data
csv_path =  paste0(getwd(), "/data/Sex_biased_gene_expression.csv")
gene_dat = read_csv(csv_path) %>%
  mutate(Chr = ifelse(Chromosome == "Z", "Z chrmosome", "Autosome"))
Parsed with column specification:
cols(
  GeneSymbol = col_character(),
  LFC.ave = col_double(),
  regulatory.function = col_character(),
  matrix.family = col_character(),
  Chromosome = col_character(),
  Coverage = col_double(),
  Direction = col_character(),
  Top10 = col_character(),
  ori = col_character(),
  catogory = col_character(),
  Group = col_character(),
  Male_biased = col_double(),
  Female_biased = col_double()
)
FWm = gene_dat %>% filter(Group == "FW", Male_biased == 1, Chr == "Autosome") %>%
  select(GeneSymbol) %>% pull()
CBm = gene_dat %>% filter(Group == "CB", Male_biased == 1, Chr == "Autosome") %>%
  select(GeneSymbol) %>% pull()
LDm = gene_dat %>% filter(Group == "LD", Male_biased == 1, Chr == "Autosome") %>%
  select(GeneSymbol) %>% pull()
SDTm = gene_dat %>% filter(Group == "SDT", Male_biased == 1, Chr == "Autosome") %>%
  select(GeneSymbol) %>% pull()
LDtoNSm = gene_dat %>% filter(Group == "LDtoNS", Male_biased == 1, Chr == "Autosome") %>%
  select(GeneSymbol) %>% pull()
SDtoNSm = gene_dat %>% filter(Group == "SDtoNS", Male_biased == 1, Chr == "Autosome") %>%
  select(GeneSymbol) %>% pull()
SDm = gene_dat %>% filter(Group == "SD", Male_biased == 1, Chr == "Autosome") %>%
  select(GeneSymbol) %>% pull()

input = list(FWm, CBm, LDm, SDTm, LDtoNSm, SDtoNSm, SDm)

fn_percent = function(i){
  j = 1:length(input)
  sapply(1:length(j), function(t){ length(intersect(input[[i]], input[[t]]))/length(input[[i]]) })
}

# push <- function(l, x) {assign(l, append(eval(as.name(l)), x), envir=parent.frame())}

# row.names(up_auto_num) = lab

          keysize = 1, col = colp,
          density.info = 'none', cexRow = 1, cexCol = 1, srtCol = 0,
          margins = c(2, 10))
